Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: I have been to Dickys Grand Café with two of my friends. We ordered finger food, which was really tasty and the service was great. Especially, as one of my friends requested some special cheese on her fries and the waitress did her best to organize it. The drinks were refreshing as well.

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Was informed that the restaurant was open for dinner and I made a reservation. When we got there they made us order right away because the kitchen was closed (even though on the phone I specifically made a reservation for dinner and was on time). Waiters were disorganized and forgot half our order. Then I found a hair in my salad.

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: The last couple of years the place has been renovated. Perfect ambiance for after work drinks

Review Text: Can imagine it's a cool place, but definitely wasn't designed for as many people as it gets

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Went for a beer between 16 and closing and the volume was ridiculously loud. Basically have to yell to your table. Staff is very friendly.

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Wonderfull as always. We noticed there was a tiny piecy of cork in one of the wine glasses. We immediately got 2 new glasses of wine and some extra pieces of hot wings to make up even further. We go out for drinks here at least once a week …

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Great place for drinks after a long working day. Good beers ( try Ij wit but not too much, strong beer with great taste). The menu is sufficient and the staff is always happy to have a word with you. Definitely a great place to relax that can get busy on Thursday, Friday and of course any other sunny day.

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Good sandwich for lunch, nice atmosphere on the terrace outside. Slightly slow service, but this was during a busy lunch, so not too much of an issue.

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Arguably the best burger place in Zuidas. Went there for the first time in an year and the quality of the Dicky's burger is still fantastic

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: One of the pillars of zuidas nightlife and Friday afternoon drinks. They have a wide selection of beers, wines and I believe also some cocktails. Additionally, they also serve some very nice snacks but also full dishes. Greta for the Friday night!

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Too much crowded on a Thursdays and Fridays. Very good place to chit chat with colleagues along with a glass of wine or a beer during the evening at this place is fun. Price is comparable to any other place close by Amsterdam Zuid. Snacks and starters are also nice, not much veg options though

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: I visited Dicky's today and can say that the food was lovely, the service was prompt and also the manager Qnca was very friendly and helpful in her demeanour and professional throughout. Will be eating here again for sure

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: Like this place a lot, cozy and romantic at the same time. Staff is really kind. The only negative thing is that it gets really crowded after work especially thursdays full of pretentious young business personnel. If you avoid the crowd, you will have good time :)

Name: Grand Café Dickys
Review Text: One of the crowded pub near busiest business place of Amsterdam zuid. Great accessibility. Spacious from both inside and outside. Good snacks. Average priced. Free wifi and good beers.
